CL-FLASH-LOANS
==============

This software was extracted from CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain).

Original Source: https://github.com/clpic/clpic
Extracted Module: src/defi/flash/

The flash loan protocol implementation provides:
- Atomic flash loan execution
- Callback interface handling
- Liquidity pool management
- Fee calculation and distribution
- Reentrancy protection

This standalone version removes all external dependencies and provides a
pure Common Lisp implementation suitable for integration into other projects.

